{"tid":208974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李私煙幫七犯籌左好多錢啊","createTime":"2017-04-20T00:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T03:24:35.000Z","uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d4dd7a296c92308597810a0ab4e243eae1e11be","tid":208974,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T00:56:49.000Z","msg":"七警各獲$7,899捐款<br />\n<br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】撐警大聯盟等團體早前發起支援七警生活費籌款，<span style=\"color: red;\">召集人李偲嫣透露，近一個月共籌得5.5萬元，每位涉案警員可分得7,899.3元，</span>下周會將款項交予七警家屬代表。負責收集捐款的經民聯成員、律師莊永燦指曾在2月去信特首梁振英要求特赦七警，對方回信稱已交相關部門參閱。<br />\n<br />\n繼多個親建制組織向警務人員及家屬捐款數千萬元後，撐警大聯盟召集人李偲嫣宣佈，與香港警察員佐級協會創建人暨退役同僚聯會於2月20日至3月15日共籌得55,295.3元支援七警，來自50多名捐款者，每位警員可獲7,899.3元，並寫了7張支票下周交家屬代表。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被問到款額是否符合預期，李承認籌得款額不多，但屬市民心意，部份屬匿名捐款，亦聲稱有人表示慳了數天早餐錢作捐款，及自稱是殘疾人士的60多歲女士特意外出到銀行捐款700元。她強調籌款不涉及收取行政費，<span style=\"color: red;\">記者問她有否捐款時，她最初僅稱「有」，笑稱不便透露金額，被追問後才指「唔係好多，4位數字」。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於民主黨主席胡志偉曾提出同時特赦七警和佔中人士，莊永燦指七警因執勤受挑釁才有錯誤行為，與佔中人士蓄意犯法不同，不能相提並論。<br />\n■記者鍾雅宜"},{"pid":"79d141e11ce1f24f245b1927f9c85b84a108c382","tid":208974,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T01:00:59.000Z","msg":"佢收左幾多行政費先？"},{"pid":"e6000dc764e5870073f98cb2e97bb627532dac17","tid":208974,"uid":12438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T01:03:17.000Z","msg":"捐錢班撚樣冇腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46acad62e4d7f03c6464c23b19a4b31018c2348b","tid":208974,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T01:05:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢收左幾多行政費先？</blockquote><br />\n人地話冇收啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e3e18475b48f13128762f943e75dcc297808e24","tid":208974,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T01:06:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢收左幾多行政費先？</blockquote><br />\n人地話冇收啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n$500一個人頭叫人去遊行都要錢啦"},{"pid":"087176c8f971884fa465be5faba9a2d2479196a6","tid":208974,"uid":86980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T01:10:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢收左幾多行政費先？</blockquote><br />\n人地話冇收啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n$500一個人頭叫人去遊行都要錢啦</blockquote><br />\n籌錢梗要還, 咪比錢中介!"},{"pid":"5e17a77b50b18c184c52f2fb31d080fbedc8f0f6","tid":208974,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T01:14:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>莊永燦指七警因執勤受挑釁才有錯誤行為，與佔中人士蓄意犯法不同，不能相提並論。</blockquote><br />\n哇我屌你老尾難聽過粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e773864a24f2dede7ef84e9b3377bc4c6c80a7","tid":208974,"uid":24781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T01:15:11.000Z","msg":"私煙: 又有錢俾我袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74554c0371cfe48f426e45014d2c78b5b8ada4f","tid":208974,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T01:16:57.000Z","msg":"佢自己收起左50萬"},{"pid":"c9520f2071d068ce75e215d392e59aed287121bf","tid":208974,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T01:21:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>莊永燦指七警因執勤受挑釁才有錯誤行為，與佔中人士蓄意犯法不同，不能相提並論。</blockquote><br />\n哇我屌你老尾難聽過粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n政府挑釁市民先有佔路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36077038ca58cea0609617f9616efb1652a4c259","tid":208974,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T01:22:14.000Z","msg":"八千都無 乞都乞到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef6f11d78a10892dd1c01d94554708522aa715b","tid":208974,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s